ston]]\n[[Category:Melbourne-related lists|Frankston people]]\n[[Category:Frankston, Victoria|People]]\n[[Category:Lists of people from Victoria (Australia)|Frankston ]]\n", "name_user": "JohnBilling3199", "label": "safe", "comment": "Added Toni Watson (Tones & I) and Billy Higgins", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_people_from_Frankston"}
